<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="run-out">run out</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>(某物) 用完；不多了；没有了</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In the future, care for the environment will become very important as earth’s natural resources run out.
在未来，爱护环境将会很重要，因为地球的资源将濒临枯竭。</p><footer>外研④ – 1</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My car broke down on the way to the beach because it had run out of petrol.
在去海滩的路上，我的车因为汽油耗尽而抛锚了。</p><footer>北师大⑥ – 16</footer></div></div>